3. WHEN ARE MARKERS EVALUATED
-------------------------------
Markers are handled at TWO distinct times:

A. PARSE TIME — marker stored on the Requirement struct
   When uv parses a PEP 508 requirement string (e.g.
   "requests>=2.0; python_version > '3.8'"), the grammar parser
   at crates/uv-pep508/src/lib.rs line 982 calls:

       let marker = if cursor.peek_char() == Some(';') {
